---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
    title="Stories - Kate Mas – Career Coach"
    description="Real stories from real people who embraced their messy careers with Kate's coaching"
>
    <div class="py-12 sm:py-16 min-h-screen">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-5 sm:px-6">
            <div class="text-center mb-10 sm:mb-16">
                <p class="font-sans text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-primary mb-4">
                    Client Stories
                </p>
                <h1 class="font-serif text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl text-foreground mb-6">
                    Stories
                </h1>
                <p class="font-sans text-base sm:text-lg text-muted-foreground max-w-2xl mx-auto">
                    Real stories from real people who embraced their messy careers.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4 sm:gap-6 max-w-6xl mx-auto">

                <!-- Yana A. -->
                <div class="bg-card p-5 sm:p-6 rounded-2xl border border-border hover:border-primary transition-colors group flex flex-col">
                    <div class="mb-5">
                        <span class="font-sans text-xs font-bold bg-secondary text-primary px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full uppercase tracking-wider">Career clarity</span>
                    </div>
                    <blockquote class="font-accent text-lg text-foreground leading-snug mb-4 flex-grow">
                        "Kate's approach helped me see myself and my potential in a new light."
                    </blockquote>
                    <details class="mb-5 group/details">
                        <summary class="font-sans text-xs font-bold text-primary/50 uppercase tracking-wider cursor-pointer list-none flex items-center gap-1.5 hover:text-primary transition-colors">
                            <svg class="w-3 h-3 transition-transform group-open/details:rotate-90" viewBox="0 0 12 12" fill="currentColor"><path d="M4 2l4 4-4 4"/></svg>
                            Read full review
                        </summary>
                        <p class="font-sans text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed mt-3">
                            "Working with Kate was an incredible and transformative experience. Over the course of just five sessions, I gained profound insights into why I was feeling stuck and uncovered several blind spots that were holding me back. Kate's deep, thoughtful, and timely questions led to many personal discoveries, some of which extended far beyond the original scope of my goals. Her ability to offer genuine support while highlighting areas where I underestimated or overly criticized myself was truly invaluable. Each session felt tailored to my unique needs, and her flexibility with scheduling made the process even smoother. Beyond her coaching skills, Kate is an incredibly warm and open person. She radiates kindness and support, creating an environment where you feel safe to explore your thoughts and challenges. I couldn't have asked for a better coach. Highly recommended!"
                        </p>
                    </details>
                    <p class="font-sans text-sm text-muted-foreground">Yana A.</p>
                </div>

                <!-- Marta R. -->
                <div class="bg-card p-5 sm:p-6 rounded-2xl border border-border hover:border-primary transition-colors group flex flex-col">
                    <div class="mb-5">
                        <span class="font-sans text-xs font-bold bg-secondary text-primary px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full uppercase tracking-wider">Career pivot</span>
                    </div>
                    <blockquote class="font-accent text-lg text-foreground leading-snug mb-4 flex-grow">
                        "She guided me to understand what will work best for me — not just following external signals and trends."
                    </blockquote>
                    <details class="mb-5 group/details">
                        <summary class="font-sans text-xs font-bold text-primary/50 uppercase tracking-wider cursor-pointer list-none flex items-center gap-1.5 hover:text-primary transition-colors">
                            <svg class="w-3 h-3 transition-transform group-open/details:rotate-90" viewBox="0 0 12 12" fill="currentColor"><path d="M4 2l4 4-4 4"/></svg>
                            Read full review
                        </summary>
                        <p class="font-sans text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed mt-3">
                            "First, I'm grateful for finding a coach like Kate and our sessions that helped me to look back into my career path with more empathy and value more what I've done. Kate helped me to bring clarity on why I was stuck in my career. I really like her approach in coaching. She was asking deep questions that made me reflect a lot on my career path. I got good insight about self validation and understanding what are my needs in the ideal work environment. She helped me to understand that each change is the process, even coaching is about the process just like therapy."
                        </p>
                    </details>
                    <p class="font-sans text-sm text-muted-foreground">Marta R.</p>
                </div>

                <!-- Anonymous -->
                <div class="bg-card p-5 sm:p-6 rounded-2xl border border-border hover:border-primary transition-colors group flex flex-col">
                    <div class="mb-5">
                        <span class="font-sans text-xs font-bold bg-secondary text-primary px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full uppercase tracking-wider">Life pivot</span>
                    </div>
                    <blockquote class="font-accent text-lg text-foreground leading-snug mb-4 flex-grow">
                        "Kate helped me dig out a much bigger problem — and move forward with a truly pivotal decision for me and my family."
                    </blockquote>
                    <details class="mb-5 group/details">
                        <summary class="font-sans text-xs font-bold text-primary/50 uppercase tracking-wider cursor-pointer list-none flex items-center gap-1.5 hover:text-primary transition-colors">
                            <svg class="w-3 h-3 transition-transform group-open/details:rotate-90" viewBox="0 0 12 12" fill="currentColor"><path d="M4 2l4 4-4 4"/></svg>
                            Read full review
                        </summary>
                        <p class="font-sans text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed mt-3">
                            "I went into the process just as an experiment, to see how coaching can help me with my work/life balance. Oh boy, how far that goal was from what really mattered. Coaching helped me to see clearly the real challenges I have, reflect back on the strategies I use to cope with them and challenge myself to do better. All the way, Kate was receptive and open in our conversation, never going into advice mode, but just gently guiding me to answer (sometimes tough) questions by myself. I especially liked the way we did course correction mid-sessions and how Kate noticed things were going South and proactively suggested a new plan that worked terrifically. That for me is a true showcase of a good work!"
                        </p>
                    </details>
                    <p class="font-sans text-sm text-muted-foreground">Anonymous</p>
                </div>

                <!-- Pauline -->
                <div class="bg-card p-5 sm:p-6 rounded-2xl border border-border hover:border-primary transition-colors group flex flex-col">
                    <div class="mb-5">
                        <span class="font-sans text-xs font-bold bg-secondary text-primary px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full uppercase tracking-wider">Self-awareness</span>
                    </div>
                    <blockquote class="font-accent text-lg text-foreground leading-snug mb-4 flex-grow">
                        "Kate's greatest talent is to uncover your belief system — and she does it at an incredible speed. That's what makes each session so effective."
                    </blockquote>
                    <details class="mb-5 group/details">
                        <summary class="font-sans text-xs font-bold text-primary/50 uppercase tracking-wider cursor-pointer list-none flex items-center gap-1.5 hover:text-primary transition-colors">
                            <svg class="w-3 h-3 transition-transform group-open/details:rotate-90" viewBox="0 0 12 12" fill="currentColor"><path d="M4 2l4 4-4 4"/></svg>
                            Read full review
                        </summary>
                        <p class="font-sans text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed mt-3">
                            "You helped me uncover, thoroughly understand and ultimately discard unhealthy beliefs that I was caught up in for a long time. First, being ambitious isn't a bad thing. It certainly doesn't mean being a self-centred person who only cares about their career and nothing else. Second, knowing one's needs and wanting certain things to meet those needs doesn't mean being ungrateful. I now want things! Third, being on the copilot's seat of someone else's life and being driven around without a wish where to go was a mental survival strategy that worked well for me for a certain period of time. Letting this idea go and being back behind the driver's steering wheel is probably the biggest change you helped me achieve. Our goal was to make me feel more alive. We certainly achieved that!"
                        </p>
                    </details>
                    <p class="font-sans text-sm text-muted-foreground">Pauline</p>
                </div>

                <!-- Daria L. -->
                <div class="bg-card p-5 sm:p-6 rounded-2xl border border-border hover:border-primary transition-colors group flex flex-col">
                    <div class="mb-5">
                        <span class="font-sans text-xs font-bold bg-secondary text-primary px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full uppercase tracking-wider">Career growth</span>
                    </div>
                    <blockquote class="font-accent text-lg text-foreground leading-snug mb-4 flex-grow">
                        "She helps you uncover solutions you didn't even know you had in you."
                    </blockquote>
                    <details class="mb-5 group/details">
                        <summary class="font-sans text-xs font-bold text-primary/50 uppercase tracking-wider cursor-pointer list-none flex items-center gap-1.5 hover:text-primary transition-colors">
                            <svg class="w-3 h-3 transition-transform group-open/details:rotate-90" viewBox="0 0 12 12" fill="currentColor"><path d="M4 2l4 4-4 4"/></svg>
                            Read full review
                        </summary>
                        <p class="font-sans text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed mt-3">
                            "Working with Kate has been an absolute game-changer! Her energy and enthusiasm create a positive and motivating atmosphere. She listens deeply, asks thought-provoking questions, and helps you uncover solutions you didn't even know you had in you. Each session feels tailored to my journey, with just the right mix of encouragement and challenge. I've seen real progress thanks to her guidance and couldn't be more grateful. Truly an exceptional coach!"
                        </p>
                    </details>
                    <p class="font-sans text-sm text-muted-foreground">Daria L.</p>
                </div>

                <!-- Myroslav -->
                <div class="bg-card p-5 sm:p-6 rounded-2xl border border-border hover:border-primary transition-colors group flex flex-col">
                    <div class="mb-5">
                        <span class="font-sans text-xs font-bold bg-secondary text-primary px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full uppercase tracking-wider">Life goals</span>
                    </div>
                    <blockquote class="font-accent text-lg text-foreground leading-snug mb-5 flex-grow">
                        "The coaching sessions helped me understand myself much better and get clarity on my life goals — something I really want."
                    </blockquote>
                    <p class="font-sans text-sm text-muted-foreground">Myroslav</p>
                </div>

                <!-- Share your story CTA -->
                <div class="bg-primary p-6 rounded-2xl flex flex-col justify-between">
                    <div>
                        <div class="mb-5">
                            <span class="font-sans text-xs font-bold bg-secondary text-primary px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full uppercase tracking-wider">Your turn</span>
                        </div>
                        <p class="font-accent italic text-lg text-primary-foreground leading-snug mb-3">
                            "We worked together — and it made a difference."
                        </p>
                        <p class="font-sans text-sm text-primary-foreground/70 leading-relaxed mb-6">
                            If you've worked with me and feel like sharing, I'd love to feature your story here. Publicly or anonymously — entirely your call.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1oJ6padQDu1aSiRP-96rQ1m67J_I6Fyrd5_D7S_K0xw4/viewform" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn-white w-full text-center">Share your story</a>
                </div>

                <!-- Mildred -->
                <div class="bg-card p-5 sm:p-6 rounded-2xl border border-border hover:border-primary transition-colors group flex flex-col">
                    <div class="mb-5">
                        <span class="font-sans text-xs font-bold bg-secondary text-primary px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full uppercase tracking-wider">Self-discovery</span>
                    </div>
                    <blockquote class="font-accent text-lg text-foreground leading-snug mb-4 flex-grow">
                        "What I found was something much deeper, more human, and incredibly impactful."
                    </blockquote>
                    <details class="mb-5 group/details">
                        <summary class="font-sans text-xs font-bold text-primary/50 uppercase tracking-wider cursor-pointer list-none flex items-center gap-1.5 hover:text-primary transition-colors">
                            <svg class="w-3 h-3 transition-transform group-open/details:rotate-90" viewBox="0 0 12 12" fill="currentColor"><path d="M4 2l4 4-4 4"/></svg>
                            Read full review
                        </summary>
                        <p class="font-sans text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed mt-3">
                            "Before starting my sessions with Kate, I had a very different idea of what coaching would be like. I expected something more like a fitness coach yelling, 'work your ass off and you can achieve anything, go, go, go!', something more structured, maybe even transactional. But what I found was something much deeper, more human, and incredibly impactful. Our conversations went beyond surface-level goals. We explored things I needed to look at: confidence, career growth after maternity leave, who I want to be as a professional, how to align with my values, and most importantly, how to reconnect with myself. Kate helped me realize that competing with others doesn't serve me, and that showing up as my full, authentic self is not only enough, but powerful. She has a remarkable ability to really listen, to catch the unspoken, and to gently but clearly bring attention to what's underneath. I felt seen, supported, and deeply understood. Her warmth and presence created a safe space that allowed me to be vulnerable, and her guidance helped me build more compassion toward myself, something I was missing. I wholeheartedly recommend working with Kate to anyone looking not just to grow, but to pause, reflect, reevaluate, reconnect, and ultimately, rediscover themselves."
                        </p>
                    </details>
                    <p class="font-sans text-sm text-muted-foreground">Mildred C.</p>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</BaseLayout>
